formance gain would be almost invisible. Roslyn favors GC-friendliness over=
 micro-optimizing where it isn=E2=80=99t needed.</p><h2 id=3D"b90f" class=
=3D"nj nk gm bg nl nm nn no np nq nr ns nt nu nv nw nx ny nz oa ob oc od oe=
 of og bl" data-selectable-paragraph=3D""><strong class=3D"an">Conclusion</=
