""><strong class=3D"ml gn">Green nodes</strong> =E2=80=94 tiny, cached, imm=
utable =E2=80=9Cbricks=E2=80=9D of the abstract-syntax tree.</li><li id=3D"=
e575" class=3D"mj mk gm ml b mm qc mo mp mq qd ms mt mu qe mw mx my qf na n=
b nc qg ne nf ng pz qa qb bl" data-selectable-paragraph=3D""><strong class=
=3D"ml gn">Red nodes</strong> =E2=80=94 handy wrappers that supply the pare=
nt link, absolute position, and an IDE-friendly API; they=E2=80=99re create=
d lazily when first requested and don=E2=80=99t cling to memory after edits=
.</li><li id=3D"7c27" class=3D"mj mk gm ml b mm qc mo mp mq qd ms mt mu qe =
mw mx my qf na nb nc qg ne nf ng pz qa qb bl" data-selectable-paragraph=3D"=
"><strong class=3D"ml gn">Bit-level packing and tiered list implementations=
</strong> keep the entire object graph extremely compact.</li></ul><p id=3D=
"cc7a" class=3D"pw-post-body-paragraph mj mk gm ml b mm mn mo mp mq mr ms m=
